Terrorsaur:





The acid rain on Terrorsaur's body washed away with the water KitKat 
poured on him. He continued to wiped at the water on his shoulders, 
thinking it was still on him. He looked at himself, seeing that the 
acid was no longer eating at his armor. He began to calm down. 

He looked at KitKat. He then turned his head as AirBomber ran out of 
the Predacon cave. The acid rain was still going on outside, and it 
looked like it would last for a while. He sneered, begining to smell 
the Vok originated rain.
